This paper deals with community detection, which is a problem in network analysis. The paper specifically focuses on the issue of statistical significance in community detection. Based on this, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), which deals with the analysis of social and information networks. Other likely sub-categories include cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SD (Software Engineering), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.LG (Machine Learning), as these sub-categories also deal with network analysis and statistical analysis.
